Header for .c files
===================

Every C file in the MIPL project (i.e. in src directory) must have
this header.  When a new file is created, you put your name as the
author.  If you significantly modify or extend a file created by
someone else, you add your name as additional author.  Having yourself
as an author implies responsibility for the content (i.e. you will be
the first to blaim if it does not work).  Do not do major changes
without consulting the author(s) first.

