Header for .h files
===================

All header files created for the MIPL project must have this header.
No copyright claims, authors, or similar should appear there, just the
revision control header.

/* $Id$ */


Header for Makefile.am
======================

Every Makefile.am must have the following header.

## $Id$
## Process this file with automake to produce Makefile.in
